Package assignment1

Class NutritionInfo

java.lang.Object
assignment1.NutritionInfo
public class NutritionInfo extends Object
Represents the nutrition facts for a single food item. This class stores various nutrient values and provides methods to compute percentages and determine if certain nutrients are a good source in the food. It also offers methods to generate human-readable reports and labels.
Author:
Jay Chao
